8:00  - 9:00  Breakfast
9:00 - 10:30 parallel breakout sessions determined by needs
10:30 - 11:00 Coffee Break
11:00 - 12:00 group session: Readings, reports and discussion
12:00 -  1:30 Lunch
1:30 - 3:00 group session: Readings, reports and discussion
3:00 - 3:30 Coffee Break
3:30 - 5:00 group session: Readings, reports and discussion
Dinner hosted by SGI/Cray (time to be determined)

